training/ - stores files used to train the model

data/ - store samples

videos/ - store pre-recorded video to be sampled
collect_video - used to collect a sample from a prerecorded video
                run using format 
                    python collect_video <filename> <gesture>

collect_webcam - used to collect a sample from webcam 
                 keys are used to indicate gestures being recorded:
                    1 - grab
                    2 - pinch open
                    3 - pinch close
                    q - quit